      "writtenOn": "2017-03-22T18:02:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You can simplify these two lines to\n\n  DCHECK(!!buffer_ ^ !!snapshot_);\n\nbut even a weirdo like me recognizes that people probably aren’t accustomed to xor in a non-bitwise context, so I’ll also offer\n\n  DCHECK(!!buffer_ !\u003d !!snapshot_);",
      "revId": "a34adb9f57d26af715dfd5bde5f3752f629150ab",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
